	<annotations>
		<text id="0" type="text/plain" rect="(-212.0, 468.0, 338.0, 228.0)" font-family="Helvetica" font-size="16">This script makes a scan on the intensity vs magnification to show that the optimum value is at 1/3.

Note that the main system can be defined using the script in the Histogram widget. Then a loop is implemented. 
</text>
		<text id="1" type="text/plain" rect="(-311.0, -110.0, 197.0, 44.0)" font-family="Helvetica" font-size="16">Source 20 keV+/- 30 eV</text>
